Deprecated

Functions with names not adhering to the paradigm of using verb phrases, or not being descriptive enough, and which have been replaced by more appropriately named functions. However, in order to not break older code they will stay around for at least some time, and a call to one of these functions is piped to the respective new function.

proxysnr-deprecated
Deprecated functions
